India’s Gujarat May Lower Solar Tariffs for Delayed Projects

-- B y   N a t a l i e   O b i k o   P e a r s o n
-- 
2011-08-12T05:00:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/india-s-gujarat-may-lower-solar-tariffs-for-delayed-projects.html
Gujarat state, home to  India ’s
biggest solar program, may lower the tariff to be paid to sun-
powered plants that aren’t built on time, D.J. Pandian,
principal secretary of the state’s Energy & Petrochemicals
Department, said in an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
